{"div":{"@xmlns":"http://www.tei-c.org/ns/1.0","@type":"article","@xml:id":"MG-1696-07_166","@resp":"wordpro","head":{"value":"Ode sur la mort de Madame la Presidente Nicolaï","id":"/div/head"},"bibl":{"title":{"value":"Mercure galant","id":"/div/bibl/title"},"#":{"value":", juillet 1696 [tome 7], p. 166-172.","id":"/div/bibl/#"}},"p":{"#1":{"value":"Vous m’avez paru touchée de la mort de Madame la Presidente Nicolaï, qu’un mal aussi prompt que violent a enlevée de la terre, au commencement de ses plus belles années. Ainsi je croy vous faire plaisir de vous envoyer des Vers qui ont esté faits sur cette mort. Ils sont de M","id":"/div/p/#1"},"hi":{"@rend":"sup","#":{"value":"r","id":"/div/p/hi/#"}},"#2":{"value":" Dader de Toulouse.","id":"/div/p/#2"}},"quote":[{"#":[{"label":{"#":[{"hi":{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"ODE","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[0]/label/#[0]/hi/#"}}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"SUR LA MORT","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[0]/label/#[2]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"de Madame la Presidente","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[0]/label/#[4]/#"}},{"lb":{}},{"#":{"value":"Nicolaï.","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[0]/label/#[6]/#"}}]}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Esprit saint, daignez promptement","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[1]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Exaucer mon humble priere,","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[1]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Eclairez mon entendement","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[1]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"D’un rayon de vostre lumiere.","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[1]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@type":"ornament","#":{"value":"***","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[2]/ab/#"}}},{"lg":{"l":[{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":" À me l’accorder aujourd’huy","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[3]/lg/l[0]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vostre gloire vous sollicite.","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[3]/lg/l[1]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Je veux chanter Nicolaï,","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[3]/lg/l[2]/#"}},{"@rend":"i","#":{"value":"Vostre plus chere favorite.","id":"/div/quote[0]/#[3]/lg/l[3]/#"}}]}},{"ab":{"@ty